This tool takes a file containing a list of password, and generates a 
brute force password list containing the passwords and combinations of the
passwords using 2 words, 3 words, etc.

brewt_gpg can attempt to decrypt a GPG encrypted file by using the generated 
passwords

$ cat test.txt
foo
bar
baz
bing

$ ./brewt.py -p test.txt
foo
bar
baz
bing
foobar
foobaz
foobing
barfoo
barbaz
barbing
bazfoo
bazbar
bazbing
bingfoo
bingbar
bingbaz
foobarbaz
foobarbing
foobazbar
foobazbing
foobingbar
foobingbaz
barfoobaz
barfoobing
barbazfoo
barbazbing
barbingfoo
barbingbaz
bazfoobar
bazfoobing
bazbarfoo
bazbarbing
bazbingfoo
bazbingbar
bingfoobar
bingfoobaz
bingbarfoo
bingbarbaz
bingbazfoo
bingbazbar
